Package: inbreedR
Title: Workflows for analysing inbreeding based on SNP or microsatellite markers
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: as.person(c(
        "Martin A. Stoffel <martin.adam.stoffel@gmail.com> [aut, cre]",
        "Mareike Esser <messer@uni-bielefeld.de> [aut]"))
Description: Methods  from this package allow (1) calculating second-order
    heterozygosity disequilibrium (g2) from  among-locus  correlations in multilocus
    population data, (2) het-het correlations and sMLH (3) sensitivity of number of markers to 
    the estimation of HFC´s.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.2.0)
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
Suggests: 
    testthat,
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
